<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Handy Heroes Confirmation</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
  <table role="presentation" style="width: 80%; background-color:#81c3c9; padding: 20px; margin: 20px auto; border-radius: 10px; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0;">
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center; padding: 20px;">
        <!-- Inner Table -->
        <table style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 10px; border: 2px solid #fafafa;">
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 30px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #1e3653;">
              
              <!-- Header -->
              <h1 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1e3653; font-size: 24px;">Hello <%= @senior.first_name %>,</h1>

              <!-- Message Content -->
              <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #1e3653;">
                Thank you for using Handy Heroes! We are excited to confirm that your new task has been successfully created.
              </p>
              <br/>
              <table style="width: 50%; margin: 0 auto; padding-left:30px; padding-right:20px; 20px; border: 3px double #f37022; border-radius: 10px;">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e3653; line-height: 1.6;">
                      <strong>Task:</strong> <%= @task.task_type %>
                    </p>
                    <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e3653; line-height: 1.6;">
                      <strong>Task ID:</strong> <%= @task.id %>
                    </p>
                    <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e3653; line-height: 1.6;">
                      <% if @task.description.present? %>
                        <strong>Description:</strong> <%= @task.description %>
                      <% end %>  
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            
              <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e3653; line-height: 1.6;">
                Handy Hero volunteers in <%= @senior.town %>, Co. <%= @senior.county %> have been notified about your task. We will let you know as soon as someone accepts it.
              </p>

              <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e3653; line-height: 1.6;">
                If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to our friendly team. Weâ€™re always here to help.
              </p>

              <!-- Footer -->
              <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e3653; line-height: 1.6;">Best regards,</p>
              <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e3653; font-weight: bold;">The Handy Heroes Team</p>

              <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #f37022; margin: 20px 0;">

              <!-- Closing Line -->
              <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e3653; text-align: center; font-style: italic;">
                Handy Heroes... Connecting Communities, One Task at a Time!
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
